{"tid":1821580,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"明報記者元朗採訪期間受襲　編輯部譴責野蠻行為","createTime":"2020-01-12T11:46:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-12T14:51:21.000Z","uid":212626,"like":32,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"a39fd9c04cb6efdbcbd693a959b59f5be27f5564","tid":1821580,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T11:46:59.000Z","msg":"一名《明報》記者採訪元朗遊行期間被人包圍及襲擊，明報編輯部對此表示譴責，批評是野蠻行為，呼籲各方尊重採訪自由。<br />\n<br />\n近百名市民下午由元朗西鐵站遊行至元朗警署，指民主黨立法會議員林卓廷早前煽動一批暴徒進入元朗，引發7.21事件。遊行期間，有《明報》記者表示，一度被遊行人士包圍要求交代身分，她表明身分後被人推撞及腳踢，又強行扯開她的口罩，最後由防暴警員介入調停。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1502389-20200112.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1502389-20200112.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=uClJ75VMDgyJ2T8QnpTVXbhWJNg3BDkm8i4jVfgHOzw%3D&h=03458110\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1502389-20200112.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=ac666a87\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1502389-20200112.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be22fd4ef72e4c926d894859641a388178ad4f08","tid":1821580,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T11:59:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35a13ecb9968b8dab2878bac900b590f596c591a","tid":1821580,"uid":210727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T11:59:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"73dec78821f14d71d96fa66433ccfe34bf8a0605","tid":1821580,"uid":210727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T11:59:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fc55848878c406c864f079f17ee71f00b409b36c","tid":1821580,"uid":82938,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T12:00:56.000Z","msg":"中聯辦煽動一批水貨客進入上水，引發暴力事件"},{"pid":"f06f0b81e4405bd